<DOCNO> XIE19980804.0014 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-04 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> 6 Killed in Ambush in S. Africa </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, August 3 (Xinhua) -- Six people were shot dead
in an ambush near Greytown in South Africa's Kwazulu-Natal
province Monday morning, South African Press Association (SAPA)
reported.
</P>
<P>
Four men and three women were traveling in an open light
delivery vehicle on their way to report a stock theft when they
were ambushed by gunmen, SAPA quoted police as saying.
</P>
<P>
One person managed to escape into the bush and survived the
attack.
</P>
<P>
Police discovered several R1 and AK-47 shells on the scene.
</P>
