<TEXT>
<P>
BAGHDAD, August 3 (Xinhua) -- Iraq on Monday said it has ended
the probe into the murder attempt against President Saddam
Hussein's eldest son Udai Saddam, the Iraqi News Agency (INA)
reported.
</P>
