<HEADLINE> Geneva to Host Fed Cup Final </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, August 4 (Xinhua) -- The Fed Cup final between
Switzerland and Spain will be held in Geneva on September 19-20,
the International Tennis Federation announced here on Tuesday.
