<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 4 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 14 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
August 5 issued by China's Central Meteorological Station at 17:00
today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 22 degrees C., max. 32 degrees C., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. 21 degrees C., max. 28 degrees C., heavy rain to
thunder showers, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. 23 degrees C., max. 32 degrees C., drizzle to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. 24 degrees C., max. 32 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chengdu: min. 24 degrees C., max. 30 degrees C., thunder
showers, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chongqing: min. 26 degrees C., max. 33 degrees C., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Kunming: min. 18 degrees C., max. 23 degrees C., moderate rain
to drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
