<HEADLINE> Australian Dollar Closes Marginally Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, August 4 (Xinhua) -- The Australian dollar gained a
little ground Tuesday but remained under pressure from the weak
Japanese yen.
</P>
<P>
Dealers said despite expectations of a busy day as a result of
Monday's bank holiday in Sydney, trade on the foreign exchange
market had been quiet.
</P>
<P>
