<HEADLINE> Chinese President Appoints New Ambassadors </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 4 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin has
appointed three new Chinese ambassadors to foreign countries
following a decision by the National People's Congress Standing
Committee, China's top legislature:
</P>
