recently been published by the Strategic Research Center of
the Turkish Foreign Ministry to refute the alleged genocide of
ethnic Armenians by Turks between 1915 and 1923.
</P>
<P>
Turkey has denied that some 1.5 million Armenians were
massacred by Turks at that time, insisting that deaths on both
sides resulted from then civil war.
</P>
